	(descr "Variscite VAR-SOM 200-pin SO-DIMM edge-connector socket (carrier side). JEDEC MO-224 Var.AB, 0.6 mm pitch, DDR2 1.8V keying, right-angle, 14 mm height. Mating sockets: TE 1565917-4, Concraft 0701A0BE52E, JST DM-7D4-H2500. Includes two M2 SoM mounting holes (62.52 mm apart, 30.45 mm from contacts; standoff MAC8 TH-1.6-3.0-M2-B, GND). Land pattern per JST DM-200P guideline - VERIFY board-lock and mounting-hole positions against the socket/SoM customer drawings before fabrication.")
